702671f-b.title: Brooklyn: 25th Street (East) - Avenue D
702671f-b.text:
412 East 25th Street at the S.W. corner of Ave. D, known as the
Cortelyou house formerly located at 1249 Flatbush.Ave., east side,
between Ditmas and Newkirk Aves., where it was occupied by 3.
Cortelyou in 1860 and by C.E. Whitehead in 1873.
About 1922.
Npgene L. Armbruster Coklection.
NEY BE REPRODUCED.
(2)
The same as plate 1, from another angle.
About 1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
